<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>For me it's looks somehow crazy that you select Rowset via $referenceMap (-&gt;findReporter(), -&gt;findEngineer(), -&gt;findVerifier()), but can't build an Join Statement with them.</p>

<p>We need to write:
$db-&gt;select()
       -&gt;from(new Bugs())
       -&gt;join('accounts', 'accounts.account_name = bugs.reported_by')
       -&gt;join('accounts', 'accounts.account_name = bugs.assigned_to')
       -&gt;join('accounts', 'accounts.account_name = bugs.verified_by');</p>

<p>instead of just</p>

<p>$db-&gt;select()
       -&gt;from(new Bugs())
       -&gt;join(new Accounts());</p>

